---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Privacy Policy Backyard Sauna Pro"
  description="Privacy policy for BackyardSaunaPro.com"
  canonical="/privacy"
>
  <article class="max-w-2xl mx-auto prose prose-stone">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-stone-900 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mb-6">Last updated: January 2025</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-6 mb-2">Information We Collect</h2>
    <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">BackyardSaunaPro.com does not collect personal information unless you voluntarily provide it (e.g., via a contact form). We may collect standard analytics data such as page views, referral sources, and browser type through third-party analytics tools.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-6 mb-2">Cookies</h2>
    <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">This site may use cookies for analytics purposes. Amazon and other affiliate partners may also set cookies on your device when you click affiliate links. We do not control third-party cookies.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-6 mb-2">Affiliate Links</h2>
    <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">This site participates in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program and other affiliate programs. When you click a product link, the retailer may set tracking cookies to attribute your purchase. We receive a commission if you make a qualifying purchase.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-6 mb-2">Third-Party Links</h2>
    <p class="text-stone-600 mb-4">This site contains links to external websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-900 mt-6 mb-2">Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-stone-600">For privacy-related questions, use our <a href="/contact" class="text-amber-700 underline">contact page</a>.</p>
  </article>
</Base>
